### ========================================
###          INVENTORY ENDPOINTS
### ========================================
### Base URL: {{apiUrl}}/inventory
### Todos requieren authGuard (cookies de sesión).
### ========================================

### ---------- LIST MOVEMENTS ----------
### Lista movimientos de inventario con filtros.
GET {{apiUrl}}/inventory?page=1&limit=20

### ---------- LIST MOVEMENTS (por producto) ----------
GET {{apiUrl}}/inventory?product_id={{productId}}&page=1&limit=20

### ---------- LIST MOVEMENTS (por tipo) ----------
GET {{apiUrl}}/inventory?movement_type=entrada&page=1&limit=20

### ---------- GET MOVEMENTS BY PRODUCT ----------
### Obtiene todos los movimientos de un producto específico.
GET {{apiUrl}}/inventory/product/{{productId}}

### ---------- CREATE MOVEMENT (entrada) ----------
### Registra una entrada de inventario.
POST {{apiUrl}}/inventory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": "{{productId}}",
  "movement_type": "entrada",
  "quantity": 50,
  "note": "Reabastecimiento proveedor"
}

### ---------- CREATE MOVEMENT (salida) ----------
### Registra una salida de inventario (ej: merma, ajuste).
POST {{apiUrl}}/inventory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": "{{productId}}",
  "movement_type": "salida",
  "quantity": 2,
  "note": "Producto dañado"
}

### ---------- CREATE MOVEMENT (ajuste) ----------
### Ajuste manual de inventario.
POST {{apiUrl}}/inventory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": "{{productId}}",
  "movement_type": "ajuste",
  "quantity": 5,
  "note": "Ajuste por conteo físico"
}

### ========================================
###           LOW STOCK ENDPOINT
### ========================================

### ---------- LOW STOCK PRODUCTS ----------
### Productos por debajo del umbral mínimo.
GET {{apiUrl}}/inventory/low-stock
